comment: /**  * Return the underlying task (typically a {@link CronTask},  * {@link FixedRateTask} or {@link FixedDelayTask}).  * @since 5.0.2  */
code: /**  * Return the underlying task (typically a {@link CronTask},  * {@link FixedRateTask} or {@link FixedDelayTask}).  * @since 5.0.2  */ public Task getTask() {     return this.task. }

comment: /**  * Trigger cancellation of this scheduled task.  */
code: /**  * Trigger cancellation of this scheduled task.  */ public void cancel() {     ScheduledFuture<?> future = this.future.     if (future != null) {         future.cancel(true).     } }
